data.description: Enter through a 2 story foyer. The home boast a large formal dining room. Beyond the foyer is a large family room and Eat-in Kitchen. The master bedroom and bath are on the first floor. The second story has 3 large bedrooms. One with a private bath. The other two share a Jack and Jill bath.  Along with all this, there is a very large loft area on the second floor as well.
